OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777410665
OL,3,CFormer teacher jailed for indecently
OL,4,Cassaulting four girls at Belfast school
OL,6,FA former teacher has been jailed after
OL,7,Findecently assaulting pupils at a
OL,8,Fsouth Belfast school in the 1970s.
OL,10,FWilliam Lloyd-Lavery of Richmond
OL,11,FAvenue, Lisburn, was handed a two-year
OL,12,Fsentence at Belfast Crown Court.
OL,14,FThe 77-year-old was found guilty in
OL,15,FJanuary of indecently assaulting four
OL,16,Fgirls at a south Belfast school in the
OL,17,F1970s.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
