FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777410665
OL,3,CFormer teacher jailed for indecently
OL,4,Cassaulting four girls at Belfast school
OL,6,FThe former history teacher was found
OL,7,Fguilty of six counts of indecent
OL,8,Fassault spanning a period when he was
OL,9,Faged in his late 20s and early 30s.
OL,11,FTwo of his victims were 13, and his
OL,12,Fvictims described being touched
OL,13,Fsexually both over and under their
OL,14,Fclothes in the school, from locations
OL,15,Fincluding the corridor as well as
OL,16,Fafter being lured to the stationery
OL,17,Fcupboard in one instance, and a
OL,18,Fstoreroom in another instance.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777410665
OL,3,CFormer teacher jailed for indecently
OL,4,Cassaulting four girls at Belfast school
OL,6,FOne described the experience as a
OL,7,F"loss of innocence which would last
OL,8,Fher to the end of her days" which
OL,9,F"destroyed her faith in teachers".
OL,11,FAnother said the assaults changed her,
OL,12,Fthat she felt ashamed and for months
OL,13,Fafter had sleeping problems which
OL,14,Fculminated in her sleeping on a
OL,15,Fmattress on the floor of her parents'
OL,16,Fbedroom, and then having to be
OL,17,Freferred to a child psychologist.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@[O]qD@AOUqD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
