FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777410665
OL,3,CFormer teacher jailed for indecently
OL,4,Cassaulting four girls at Belfast school
OL,6,FLloyd-Lavery went on to work at
OL,7,FStormont as a researcher, speech
OL,8,Fwriter and press officer for the
OL,9,FUlster Unionist Party until his
OL,10,Fretirement in 2017.
OL,12,FSpeaking outside court, a UUP
OL,13,Fspokesman said Lloyd-Lavery worked for
OL,14,Fsome individual MLAs but was not a
OL,15,Fparty staff member.
OL,17,FOn Tuesday, Lloyd-Lavery sat in the
OL,18,Fdock with his head bowed for most of
OL,19,Fthe hearing.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777410665
OL,3,CFormer teacher jailed for indecently
OL,4,Cassaulting four girls at Belfast school
OL,6,FA number of his victims sat in the
OL,7,Fpublic gallery behind him. They hugged
OL,8,Feach other following the conclusion of
OL,9,Fthe hearing.
OL,11,FA defence barrister had requested a
OL,12,Fdelayed sentence, telling the court
OL,13,Fhis client suffers from hypertension
OL,14,Fand was at an increased risk of a
OL,15,Fstroke.
OL,17,FThe prosecution said the defendant has
OL,18,Fconsistently denied the matters, and
OL,19,Fsaid a suspended sentence would "have
OL,20,Fno effect on him".
OL,26,@{D@aOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
