PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777410665
OL,3,CFormer teacher jailed for indecently
OL,4,Cassaulting four girls at Belfast school
OL,6,FShe said a medical "can't be a get out
OL,7,Fof jail free card".
OL,9,FJudge Patrick Lynch told Lloyd-Lavery
OL,10,Fthat by his actions he "violated that
OL,11,Ftrust in the grossest manner and the
OL,12,Fcourt cannot but take the most serious
OL,13,Fview of these offences".
OL,15,FHe said the victims are to be
OL,16,Fcomplimented for coming forward to
OL,17,F"expose a paedophile".
OL,26,@nD@TOUoD@RO]rD@XOUuD@WO]yD@AOUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
