PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777410665
OL,3,CFormer teacher jailed for indecently
OL,4,Cassaulting four girls at Belfast school
OL,6,F"It may be that Lloyd-Lavery now
OL,7,Fconstitutes no danger to children, but
OL,8,F(to) emphasise that child abusers, or
OL,9,Fthose who may be tempted to abuse
OL,10,Fchildren, that they will never be able
OL,11,Fto rest easy for the crime will or may
OL,12,Fcatch up with them even decades after
OL,13,Fthe perpetration of those crimes," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"They will forever be looking over
OL,17,Ftheir shoulders in fear of that day of
OL,18,Freckoning coming."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@bO]xD@AOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
