FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777410665
OL,3,CFormer teacher jailed for indecently
OL,4,Cassaulting four girls at Belfast school
OL,6,FHe said he is imposing one concurrent
OL,7,Fsentence to reflect all the offences,
OL,8,Fof two years in prison on all counts
OL,9,Fto run concurrently.
OL,11,FSpeaking outside court, Detective
OL,12,FInspector Kelly Foley said: "This man
OL,13,Fwas an opportunist, using his position
OL,14,Fof power and trust within the school
OL,15,Fenvironment to prey on young girls.
OL,17,F"He thought for a long time he had got
OL,18,Faway with this, today has proven that
OL,19,Fthe passage of time has no bearing on
OL,20,Fa criminal justice outcome.
OL,26,@tD@]OUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
