FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777410665
OL,3,CFormer teacher jailed for indecently
OL,4,Cassaulting four girls at Belfast school
OL,6,F"I want to thank the bravery of the
OL,7,Fvictims in coming forward.
OL,9,F"We have seen an increase in reports
OL,10,Fof non-recent child abuse over the
OL,11,Flast five years, with an average of 76
OL,12,Fnew referrals of this type each month
OL,13,Facross the province.
OL,15,F"Sentencings like today, I hope, will
OL,16,Fprovide those who have suffered with
OL,17,Fthe confidence to break the years of
OL,18,Fsilence they have endured.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
