CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777410665
OL,3,CFormer teacher jailed for indecently
OL,4,Cassaulting four girls at Belfast school
OL,6,F"Let this serve as another warning to
OL,7,Fthose perpetrating child sexual abuse
OL,8,Fin our communities, we are working
OL,9,Fevery day to break down reporting
OL,10,Fbarriers and encourage victims to come
OL,11,Fforward.
OL,13,F"Our specialist officers are working
OL,14,Fday and night to relentless pursue
OL,15,Foffenders and bring them to justice."
OL,17,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
